      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes a method to allow DNS Operators to more easily update DNSSEC Key Signing Keys using the DNS as a communication channel.  The technique described is aimed at delegations in which it is currently hard to move information from the Child to Parent.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
